      <description>&lt;h1 class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;YDwarf&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;div id=&#34;outline-container-headline-1&#34; class=&#34;outline-2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;headline-1&#34;&gt;&#xA;Introduction&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div id=&#34;outline-text-headline-1&#34; class=&#34;outline-text-2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;YDwarf&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; is a minimal and cold blue CSS theme created by &lt;a href=&#34;https://emsenn.net&#34;&gt;emsenn&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div id=&#34;outline-container-headline-2&#34; class=&#34;outline-3&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;headline-2&#34;&gt;&#xA;License and Editorial Information&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div id=&#34;outline-text-headline-2&#34; class=&#34;outline-text-3&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This document and the source code it contains are released under the&#xA;MIT License and maintained at &lt;a href=&#34;https://git.sr.ht/~emsenn/ydwarf&#34;&gt;https://git.sr.ht/~emsenn/ydwarf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div id=&#34;outline-container-headline-3&#34; class=&#34;outline-2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;headline-3&#34;&gt;&#xA;Design Philosophy&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div id=&#34;outline-text-headline-3&#34; class=&#34;outline-text-2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The &lt;em&gt;YDwarf&lt;/em&gt; theme is based on a client&amp;#39;s request for a website which&#xA;would have a landing page containing a sales-letter, a second&#xA;sales-letter, and finally a link to a form page.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
